課程學習目標 Course Objectives
To acquaint students with the development of Kansei Engineering in designTo have students think about people's Kansei needs and how they can be satisfiedTo have students explore the application of Kansei in various design subjectsTo have students criticize, debate, and communicate advanced design topics 

